flowchart TD
    U[User Prompt] --> G[/POST /generate/]
    G --> O[Ollama Generate]
    O --> V[YamlValidationPipeline]
    V -->|invalid| F[FeedbackItem]
    F --> A[/POST /ask/]
    A --> O

    V -->|valid YAML| S[SessionStore]
    S --> E[/POST /execute/]
    E --> T[TemplateSelector]
    T --> C[LuaCodeGenerator]
    C --> L[LuaCodeValidator luac -p]
    L -->|ok| X[DockerSandboxExecutor]
    L -->|syntax error| ER[409 NormalizedValidationError]

    X -->|success/failed/timeout| R[ExecutionResult]
    R --> API[FastAPI JSON Response]
    API --> UI[Web UI index.html]
